path

使用 Google 地圖的標記（marker）與路徑（path）

d <- function(x=-95.36, y=29.76, n,r,a){
  round(data.frame(
    lon = jitter(rep(x,n), amount = a),
    lat = jitter(rep(y,n), amount = a)
  ), digits = r)
}
df <- d(n = 50,r = 3,a = .3)
map <- get_googlemap(markers = df, path = df,, scale = 2)
